    </div>
    <div>
      <h4>Follow Us</h4>
      <a href="#"><svg class="footer-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 2H2v20h20V2z"/></svg>Facebook</a>
      <a href="#"><svg class="footer-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6 2 2 6 2 12s4 10 10 10 10-4 10-10S18 2 12 2z"/></svg>Instagram</a>
      <a href="#"><svg class="footer-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 4.01c-0.77 0.34-1.6 0.57-2.46 0.67 0.89-0.53 1.57-1.37 1.88-2.37-0.83 0.49-1.75 0.84-2.72 1.03C18.53 2.48 17.29 2 16 2c-3.36 0-6.08 2.72-6.08 6.08 0 0.48 0.05 0.94 0.16 1.38-5.04-0.25-9.51-2.67-12.5-6.36-0.52 0.88-0.82 1.91-0.82 3.01 0 2.08 1.06 3.91 2.66 4.98-0.99-0.03-1.92-0.3-2.74-0.75v0.08c0 2.9 2.06 5.33 4.8 5.88-0.5 0.14-1.02 0.21-1.56 0.21-0.38 0-0.75-0.04-1.11-0.11 0.75 2.33 2.92 4.03 5.5 4.08-2.02 1.58-4.56 2.52-7.32 2.52-0.48 0-0.96-0.03-1.43-0.08 2.63 1.69 5.75 2.68 9.09 2.68 10.91 0 16.87-9.04 16.87-16.87 0-0.26-0.01-0.51-0.02-0.77 1.16-0.83 2.17-1.87 2.96-3.06z"/></svg>Twitter</a>
      <a href="#"><svg class="footer-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16.98 3.3c-0.12-0.24-0.31-0.45-0.56-0.56-0.49-0.24-1.58-0.53-3.14-0.53-1.57 0-2.65 0.29-3.14 0.53-0.24 0.12-0.45 0.32-0.56 0.56-0.25 0.49-0.55 1.58-0.55 3.14 0 1.57 0.3 2.65 0.55 3.14 0.11 0.24 0.32 0.45 0.56 0.56 0.49 0.25 1.58 0.55 3.14 0.55s2.65-0.3 3.14-0.55c0.24-0.11 0.45-0.32 0.56-0.56 0.25-0.49 0.55-1.58 0.55-3.14s-0.3-2.65-0.55-3.14zM12 8.3c-2.03 0-3.68 1.65-3.68 3.68s1.65 3.68 3.68 3.68 3.68-1.65 3.68-3.68-1.65-3.68-3.68-3.68z"/></svg>WhatsApp</a>
